Metacritic Score Scraper v0.1
-----------------------------

Accepted command line arguments: -c, -f, -h (default), or -help

-c: reads input from csv (game,console) and writes to a new csv
-f: reads input from file (game:console) and writes to a new file
-h: prompts user to enter data (game:console) and outputs to terminal
-help: prints this info on screen

Written by Assil Ksiksi

Note: to run this, you'll need httplib2. Get it from here:

http://code.google.com/p/httplib2/